        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued September 8 at 10:56PM CDT until September 9 at 12:00AM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>SVRAMA

The National Weather Service in Amarillo has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Northwestern Gray County in the Panhandle of Texas...

* Until midnight CDT.

* At 1055 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 5 miles east of
Pampa, moving south at 10 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.
Hail damage to vehicles is expected.

* Locations impacted include...
Pampa and Lefors.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
